<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>旅遊趣 | 全臺飯店民宿資訊</title>
    <link
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
      <header class="mb-auto">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-0">
          <h3 class="float-md-left mb-0">旅遊趣</h3>
          <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-right">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">首頁</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/hotels">優質旅宿</a>
            <% if(!currentUser){ %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">登入</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/register">註冊</a>
            <% }else{ %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">登出</a>
            <% } %>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>
      <main class="px-3">
        <h1>旅遊趣</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          歡迎來到旅遊趣! <br />
          立即加入，探索我們眾多的民宿飯店地點。<br />
          也歡迎分享您自己的旅宿經驗，並留言評論其他人的分享！
        </p>
        <a
          href="/hotels"
          class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold bg-white"
          >開始探索</a
        >
      </main>
      <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
        <p>&copy; travelfun 2024</p>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
